				\begin{document}$$ {d}_{ppc}={c}_p\left[\frac{\left({M}_{post,T}-{M}_{pre,T}\right)-\left({M}_{post,C}-{M}_{pre,C}\right)}{SD_{pre}}\right] $$\end{document}dppc=cpMpost,T−Mpre,T−Mpost,C−Mpre,CSDpre

